  "description": "Hybrid framework for enterprise software planning and building. Core is a structured prompt system for LLM coding agents (Cursor, Claude Code, Kimi Code, Windsurf), complemented by standalone executable tools: ADR Validator, Microtask Linter, and CI/CD quality gate templates.",
